ActPublic Sector Pension Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of M. MARIANNE HARRIS of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Public Sector Pension Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Lynn Haight, whose term has expired.
